---
import Base from "~/layouts/Base.astro";
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Contact — Matthias Wesolowski · Wedecom Consulting GmbH"
  description="Get in touch with Wedecom Consulting GmbH. Founder-led by Matthias Wesolowski, helping product and engineering teams improve delivery with AI-assisted engineering."
>
  <article class="md pt-12 pb-20 md:pt-16 md:pb-24">
    <h1 class="md-title">Contact</h1>

    <Section label="Reach me" id="reach">
      <div class="md-prose">
        <p>
          A short conversation is usually enough to know whether the fit is
          right. Tell Wedecom what you are trying to ship, where delivery is
          slow, and where AI could shorten the loop. Matthias reads every
          message and works in English and German, with clients across Europe
          and especially DACH.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-7">
        <p class="md-arrow">
          <a href="mailto:info@wedecom-consulting.de" class="ink-link">info@wedecom-consulting.de</a>
        </p>
        <p class="md-arrow">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthias-wesolowski-320b033b/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ink-link">
            linkedin.com/in/matthias-wesolowski ↗
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <Section label="Office" id="office">
      <div class="md-prose">
        <p>
          Wedecom Consulting GmbH<br />
          Estostr. 13A · 82140 Olching, near Munich, Germany<br />
          HRB 229467 · Amtsgericht München
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </article>
</Base>
